            ## Simple use
            hz-tooltip allows to create tooltip as resources with all the advantages of an haztivity resource.
            hz-tooltip uses [tooltipster](http://iamceege.github.io/tooltipster/) under the hood.
            ### Usage
            1. Set data-hz-resource to the trigger element (the element that has the tooltip)
            2. Set the title attribute with the text for the tooltip

            ```html
            <button data-hz-resource="HzTooltip" title="Tooltip content!"> Hover me! </button>
            ```
        button(data-hz-resource="HzTooltip" title="Tooltip content!") Hover me!

