            ### Template
            For more complex tooltips tooltipster allow to include html in the tooltip using templates.

            ```html
            <button data-hz-resource="HzTooltip" data-tooltip-content="#tooltip-content"> HTML Content </button>
            <div class=".tooltip-template">
                <p id="tooltip-content">
                    <img src="./pages/6611/assets/images/rocket.png"/>
                </p>
            </div>
            ```

            For more info see [the doc](https://iamceege.github.io/tooltipster/#html)

